---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import headshot from '../assets/headshot.jpeg';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Connor Hanify - Security Engineer at Databricks"
  description="Connor Hanify is a Security Engineer at Databricks, specializing in incident response, cloud security, and cybersecurity. Previously at Uber and Aon Cyber Solutions."
  activeNav="about"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Connor Hanify",
      "url": "https://connorhanify.com",
      "jobTitle": "Security Engineer",
      "worksFor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Databricks" },
      "sameAs": [
        "https://github.com/cchanify",
        "https://www.linkedin.com/in/connor-hanify-848063114/",
        "https://www.strava.com/athletes/chanify"
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <div class="intro">
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>I am currently a Security Engineer at Databricks, where I am part of the incident response team. Before this, I worked on the security team at Uber, and as a Cyber Security Consultant at Aon Cyber Solutions (formerly Stroz Friedberg). I graduated from Middlebury College in 2019 with a Computer Science degree and Political Philosophy minor. At Middlebury I captained the <a href="http://sites.middlebury.edu/ultimate/2018/06/18/middlebury-guy-pranksters-2018-season-recap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Middlebury Men's Ultimate Frisbee Team 2018 season recap">Men's Ultimate Frisbee Team</a>, participated in our computer science club, MiddleEndian, and tutored CS students.</p>
    </div>
    <Image class="headshot" src={headshot} alt="Connor Hanify" width={440} />
  </div>

  <p>I'm interested in technology, especially in products that help people live better. I am particularly curious about security, AI, biotech, and renewable energy, although I'm always ready to learn new things. I'm a fan of the <a href="https://www.dreamsongs.com/RiseOfWorseIsBetter.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Worse Is Better UNIX philosophy">Worse Is Better</a> UNIX philosophy and a lover of minimalism.</p>

  <p>I also like to <a href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/chanify" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Connor's Strava profile">bike, swim, and run</a>.</p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .intro-text {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .intro-text p {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .headshot {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .intro {
      flex-direction: column-reverse;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .headshot {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
    }
  }
</style>
